snippet.title: 14.0 Heavy Duty | Gameplay Trailer | SCP: Secret Laboratory
snippet.description:
The 14.0 “Heavy Duty” update is now public! Featuring new human models, completely revamped heavy containment zone, and the reworked reinforcements system.

Play the game for free: https://store.steampowered.com/app/700330/SCP_Secret_Laboratory/
Patreon page: https://patreon.scpslgame.com
Webpage: http://scpslgame.com

Credits: 
Editing and coordination by Tamer & Spooky
Assisted by x3j50 (https://bsky.app/profile/x3j50.bsky.social), Lysol and Noname
Music by Cornel "TheChemicalWolf" Kotze
